## Notes: Tracks party/raid cooldowns on raid frames.
## Author: Kasta
## Version: 1.5.1
## SavedVariables: KastaCDDB

# 1. Entry point: addon identity, version global, load message
KastaCD.lua

# 2. Shared constants + class metadata (declares the global SPELL_DB
#    table that every Classes\*.lua file appends into - no dependencies)
KastaCD_SpellDB.lua

# 3. Class spell definitions are now appended directly to KastaCD_SpellDB.lua above.

# 4. SavedVariables / profile management + spec-detection/gating
#    (depends on SpellDB + Classes for SPELL_DB contents)
KastaCD_DB.lua

# 5. Core tracking, icon building, layout (depends on DB + SpellDB)
KastaCD_Tracking.lua

# 6. Combat log handler (depends on Tracking)
KastaCD_CombatLog.lua

# 6b. Interrupt tracker (independent anchor, class-colored bars)
KastaCD_Interrupts.lua

# 6c. Crowd-control tracker (independent anchor, class-colored bars)
KastaCD_CC.lua

# 7. Settings UI (depends on DB + Tracking)
KastaCD_UI.lua

# 8. Event frame + slash command + SpecPollTicker (depends on
#    everything above)
KastaCD_Events.lua

# 9. Debug commands: /kcddebug  /kcdlevel  /kcdspec  (depends on
#    everything above)
KastaCD_Debug.lua
